===========


yarn : yet another resource negotiator

hbase on hdfs : like bigtable on top of google file system

hbase : column oriented data store (hadoop database)
support random realtime CRUD

rows are associated with column families
cell values are versioned

Value = Table + rowkey + column_family + column + timestamp

sharding - range of rows stored together


Hive keeps metadata in rdbms - derby lightweight
